<br />\nMcKinley高中合唱團曾有過輝煌的過去，他們是這個領域中的佼佼者。隨著歲月的流逝，合唱團緋聞不斷，醜聞纏身，很多富有才華的年輕人都悄然離開了。現在，這個合唱團成了&ldquo;南郭先生&rdquo;和孤僻學生的&ldquo;避風港&rdquo;。生性樂觀的Will接受了校長交辦的這項艱鉅任務：重塑McKingley合唱團的形象，創造另一次輝煌。 Will並不孤獨－－因為他有漂亮女教師Emma Pillsbury（Jayma Mays扮演）的全力輔佐<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=61363a34\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d70f4089\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3eb97877d268aa368c703cf105a47314beae1d","tid":616522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:34:55.000Z","msg":"V台收左皮"},{"pid":"9efa19c4daaf71d50d929b9a806c149f575afea9","tid":616522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a351dff7341d0803f53b3c67ab345f51da0c4f4","tid":616522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0542960b98e54cd83b6a0b304084606944651a","tid":616522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re